sop_7_node_1_5_msg_1:
You can check your bills by clicking on the button below.

The current bill will only reflect orders who have been in Completed status before your billing date in the current month.

For example: if your billing date is 25th of each month, and you ordered the item on 10 Jan, but order is only moved to completed status on 27 Jan, this order will be billed on 25 Feb, not 25 Jan.
